<para style="q1">

<verse number="9" style="v" />Before your pots can feel the thorn's burning heat,</para>

<para style="q1">he will take them away with a whirlwind, the green thorns and the burning thorns alike.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="10" style="v" />The righteous will rejoice when he sees God's vengeance;</para>

<para style="q1">he will wash his feet in the blood of the wicked,</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="11" style="v" />so that men will say, "Truly, there is a reward for the righteous person;</para>

<para style="q1">truly there is a God who judges the earth."</para>
